From: Peter Zijlstra <peterz@infradead.org>
Date: Wed, 17 Jan 2018 22:34:34 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] x86/speculation, objtool: Annotate indirect calls/jumps for
 objtool
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 4.15.10
Git-commit: 9e0e3c5130e949c389caabc8033e9799b129e429

commit 9e0e3c5130e949c389caabc8033e9799b129e429 upstream.

Annotate the indirect calls/jumps in the CALL_NOSPEC/JUMP_NOSPEC
alternatives.

